{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"cecf5cc06c","title":"首都红卫兵纠察队队员六项守则","origin":"发表于首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部：《首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部通令集（1-10）》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b110fb44a4","index":0,"year":1966,"month":8,"day":25,"articleId":"cecf5cc06c"}],"tags":[{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"ab9d2f4a37","name":"首都红卫兵纠察队西城分队指挥部"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8e0560b9f5","type":"title","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队队员六项守则","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"457724fa44","type":"authors","text":"首都红卫兵纠察队西城分队指挥部","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"4e069e26c5","type":"paragraph","text":"一、 坚决按照毛主席的指示办事。努力学习最高指示，忠实执行最高指示，热情宣传最高指示，勇敢捍卫最高指示。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"e214e06666","type":"paragraph","text":"坚决按十六条精神办事。学习十六条，熟悉十六条，掌握十六条，运用十六条。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"4ab441d5cb","type":"paragraph","text":"二、 大学解放军，大力发扬“三八作风”，雷厉风行，坚决做到：召之即来，来之能战，战之能胜。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"25cbd66818","type":"paragraph","text":"三、 必须坚决贯彻“三大纪律八项注意”。严禁打人及变相体罚，严禁侮辱人。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"74a66cf826","type":"paragraph","text":"四、 谦虚、谨慎、戒骄戒躁、全心全意为人民服务，做人民忠实的勤务员。坚决防止特殊化。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"8ef41f1d75","type":"paragraph","text":"五、 只有值勤时戴臂章，不值勤时一律不准戴臂章，臂章由班长掌握。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"ac8a7e9752","type":"paragraph","text":"六、 一定要注意深入调查研究，在任何情况下，都要沉着、冷静，严防阶级敌人乘机捣乱破坏。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"84cf7ebe03","type":"paragraph","text":" 首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"},{"id":"5fc3cdf30b","type":"paragraph","text":"（发表于首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部：《首都红卫兵纠察队西城指挥部通令集（1-10）》）","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c"}],"page":{"id":"27457e3d06","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"cecf5cc06c","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}